@startuml Arquitectura de Contenedores - Sistema de Teleprompter

title Arquitectura de Comunicación Multi-Contenedor\nSistema de Teleprompter v2.0

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false

' Definir estilos
skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<frontend>> #E3F2FD
    BorderColor<<frontend>> #1976D2
    BorderThickness<<frontend>> 2
    FontColor<<frontend>> #000000
    
    BackgroundColor<<backend>> #E8F5E9
    BorderColor<<backend>> #388E3C
    BorderThickness<<backend>> 2
    FontColor<<backend>> #000000
    
    BackgroundColor<<database>> #FFF9C4
    BorderColor<<database>> #F57C00
    BorderThickness<<database>> 2
    FontColor<<database>> #000000
    
    BackgroundColor<<cicd>> #FFEBEE
    BorderColor<<cicd>> #C62828
    BorderThickness<<cicd>> 2
    FontColor<<cicd>> #000000
}

skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
    BorderColor #424242
    BorderThickness 2
}

' Usuarios externos
actor "👤 Operador\n(Teleprompter)" as operator
actor "👤 Productor\n(Gestión Scripts)" as producer

' Contenedores
package "🌐 Docker Network: teleprompter-network" as network {
    
    rectangle "**FRONTEND**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n⚛️ React + Vite\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ Operator View\n✓ Producer View\n✓ Login\n\n🔌 Puertos:\n→ 5173 (Dev)\n→ 4173 (Preview)" as frontend <<frontend>>
    
    rectangle "**BACKEND**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🟢 Node.js + Express\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ API REST (42 endpoints)\n✓ WebSocket Server\n✓ JWT Auth\n✓ Business Logic\n\n🔌 Puertos:\n→ 3000 (API)\n→ 3001 (WebSocket)" as backend <<backend>>
    
    rectangle "**MONGODB**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🍃 MongoDB 7.0\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ 8 Collections\n✓ Índices optimizados\n✓ Transacciones ACID\n\n🔌 Puerto:\n→ 27017\n\n🔐 Credenciales:\nadmin:admin123" as mongo <<database>>
    
    rectangle "**JENKINS**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n🔨 Jenkins LTS\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✓ CI/CD Server\n✓ Pipelines automáticos\n✓ Build & Deploy\n✓ Testing\n\n🔌 Puertos:\n→ 8080 (Web)\n→ 50000 (Agent)" as jenkins <<cicd>>
}

' Volúmenes persistentes
database "💾 mongo-data\n(Volumen Docker)" as mongoVol
database "💾 jenkins-data\n(Volumen Docker)" as jenkinsVol

' Comunicación entre usuarios y frontend
operator -down-> frontend : **📡 HTTP**\nhttp://localhost:5173/operator\n\n• Ver scripts en runorder\n• Controlar teleprompter\n• Ajustar velocidad/tamaño
producer -down-> frontend : **📡 HTTP**\nhttp://localhost:5173/producer\n\n• Crear/editar scripts\n• Gestionar biblioteca\n• Aprobar contenido

' Comunicación Frontend <-> Backend
frontend -down-> backend #1976D2 : **🔵 1. HTTP REST API**\nhttp://backend:3000/api\n\n**Endpoints principales:**\n• GET/POST /scripts\n• GET/POST /runorders\n• POST /auth/login\n• GET /config\n\n**Headers:**\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>

frontend -down-> backend #388E3C : **🟢 2. WebSocket**\nws://backend:3000\n\n**Events emit:**\n• sync:teleprompter\n• sync:runorder\n\n**Events listen:**\n• script:created\n• script:updated\n• script:deleted\n• sync:teleprompter

' Comunicación Backend <-> MongoDB
backend -down-> mongo #F57C00 : **🟡 MongoDB Protocol**\nmongodb://admin:admin123@mongo:27017/teleprompter\n\n**Operaciones:**\n• CRUD Scripts\n• CRUD RunOrders\n• CRUD Users\n• Transactions\n\n**Collections:**\nscripts, runorders, users,\nconfigurations, macros,\nsessions, audits, locks

' Comunicación Jenkins
jenkins -up-> frontend #1976D2 : **🔨 Docker Build**\n\ndocker-compose build frontend\ndocker-compose up -d frontend\n✓ Health check

jenkins -up-> backend #388E3C : **🔨 Docker Build**\n\ndocker-compose build backend\ndocker-compose up -d backend\n✓ Health check

' Volúmenes
mongo -left-> mongoVol : **💾 Persistencia**\n/data/db
jenkins -right-> jenkinsVol : **💾 Persistencia**\n/var/jenkins_home

' Notas adicionales
note right of frontend #FFFDE7
**📦 Tecnologías Frontend:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
• React 18.3
• TypeScript 5.x
• Vite 6.3.5
• TailwindCSS 3.x
• Radix UI
• Socket.IO Client 4.x
• Axios
• React Router DOM
end note

note right of backend #F1F8E9
**📦 Tecnologías Backend:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
• Node.js 18-alpine
• Express 4.21.2
• Socket.IO 4.8.1
• Mongoose 8.8.4
• JWT (jsonwebtoken)
• bcryptjs
• Multer (uploads)
• Morgan (logging)
end note

note right of mongo #FFF3E0
**📦 MongoDB Collections:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
1. scripts (guiones)
2. runorders (orden emisión)
3. users (usuarios)
4. configurations (config)
5. macros (atajos)
6. sessions (JWT refresh)
7. audits (logs)
8. locks (concurrencia)
end note

note left of jenkins #FCE4EC
**📦 Jenkins Pipelines:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
**1. Frontend Build**
   • npm ci
   • npm run lint
   • npm run build
   • npm test

**2. Backend Build**
   • npm ci
   • npm run lint
   • npm test

**3. Full Deployment**
   • docker-compose down
   • docker-compose build
   • docker-compose up -d
   • health checks
end note

' Leyenda
legend bottom left
**📊 TABLA DE COMUNICACIÓN**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
|= 🔌 Tipo |= 📡 Protocolo |= 🚪 Puerto |= 🎯 Uso |
| HTTP REST API | HTTP/1.1 | 3000 | CRUD Operations |
| WebSocket | WS | 3000/3001 | Real-time Sync |
| MongoDB | Wire Protocol | 27017 | Database |
| Frontend Dev | HTTP/1.1 | 5173 | Development |
| Frontend Prev | HTTP/1.1 | 4173 | Preview Build |
| Jenkins Web | HTTP/1.1 | 8080 | CI/CD Interface |
| Jenkins Agent | TCP | 50000 | Build Agents |

**⚡ SINCRONIZACIÓN EN TIEMPO REAL:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
✓ **Operador ↔ Productor:** WebSocket bidireccional
✓ **Multi-usuario:** Cambios se propagan automáticamente
✓ **Estado compartido:** Teleprompter, RunOrder, Scripts
✓ **Latencia:** < 50ms en red local

**🔐 SEGURIDAD:**
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
✓ JWT Authentication (1h access, 7d refresh)
✓ MongoDB con usuario/password
✓ Red Docker aislada (bridge network)
✓ CORS configurado en backend
endlegend

@enduml
